  <Strings>
    <Section>Main Text</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>まずは言葉遣いからだな。
もっと綺麗な話し方を心がけようぜ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>First off, we gotta start with your words.
Remember to use nicer words.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>13</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>なんでそんな事しなきゃいけねぇんだよ。
うぜー</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Why should I have to do something like that?
So annoying.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>16</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ああ、マジうぜェ。
話し方なんざ個人の自由だろうがよ、クソが</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Yeah, that's seriously annoying. How someone
talks is their own personal freedom, shithead.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>21</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>お前ら、本当にヒドイ話し方するなぁ。
こりゃ先は長そうだぜ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You guys have such a nasty way of talking.
Looks like this is gonna be a long one.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>13</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>でも安心しろよな！
お前らが更生するまで
毎日おれが付き合ってやるから</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>But be at ease! I'll hang with you guys
every day until you've seen the light.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>13</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>マジで勘弁しろ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Seriously, gimme a break here...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>21</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ピーチパイ、先に食ってるぞ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I've already started eating my peach pie...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>12</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
